* Iron Raptor opened a small compartment in her armor at her thigh, putting 
the maximal matrix into it and then sefely shutting it away. She could sense 
the tension in the air and it was beginning to build up, even noticing 
Tavatron beside her getting uneasy.
Iron Raptor glanced at Tavatron after hearing her growl.*

" Easy....."

* She knew that it was a strain but they had to wait just a little 
longer...just a little bit.
Iron Raptor suddenly looked down as a voice caught her attention.*

" Yes, I'm the commander."

* She said to Cheetor quickly before she saw the bot relax.*
